        <Summary xml:lang="en">Utility library for gitignore style pattern matching of file paths</Summary>
        <Description xml:lang="en">pathspec is a utility library for pattern matching of file paths. So far this only includes Git&apos;s wildmatch pattern matching which itself is derived from Rsync&apos;s wildmatch. Git uses wildmatch for its gitignore files.
</Description>
